sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant R as 业务请求/Goroutine
    participant P as pgxpool
    participant C as pgx Frontend
    participant B as Backend Process
    participant Q as Parser/Planner/Executor
    participant M as Shared Memory
    participant O as OS/Storage

    R->>P: Acquire(ctx)
    alt 有空闲连接
        P-->>R: *pgxpool.Conn
    else 池已满
        R->>P: 在有界队列等待
        P-->>R: 获得连接或 ctx 超时
    end

    R->>C: Query/Exec(ctx, SQL, $1...)
    C->>B: Parse
    B->>Q: 语法解析与语义分析
    C->>B: Bind + Describe + Execute + Sync
    B->>Q: Rewrite + Plan + Execute
    Q->>M: Snapshot/Lock/ProcArray/Buffer 请求

    alt shared_buffers 命中
        M-->>Q: Buffer
    else 缓冲区未命中
        Q->>O: smgr I/O 请求
        Note over Q,O: [PG18] 某些路径可批量异步发起
        O-->>M: 数据页
        M-->>Q: Buffer
    end

    alt SELECT
        Q-->>B: 结果行
        B-->>C: RowDescription/DataRow/CommandComplete
    else UPDATE
        Q->>M: 修改 Buffer + 生成 WAL
        M->>O: WAL write/flush（按提交策略）
        O-->>B: 持久性条件满足
        B-->>C: CommandComplete
    end

    B-->>C: ReadyForQuery
    C-->>R: rows / command tag / error
    R->>P: Release
